OL,3,CSix men found guilty of rioting in
OL,4,CEly, Cardiff, after deaths of teenage
OL,5,Cboys
OL,7,FFollowing a four and a half week trial
OL,8,Fat Newport Crown Court, Lee Robinson,
OL,9,F38, of Caerau, Luke Williams, 31, of
OL,10,FEly, Jaydan Baston, 21, of Caerau,
OL,11,FJordan Bratcher, 27, of Ely, Zayne
OL,12,FFarrugia, 25, of Caerau, and Connor
OL,13,FO'Sullivan, 26, of Caerau were all
OL,14,Ffound guilty of rioting.
OL,16,FMcKenzie Danks, 22, of Caerau, was
OL,17,Ffound not guilty of the same charge.
OL,18,FAll seven defendants had previously
OL,19,Fdenied the charges.
