OL,7,FMcKenzie Danks had previously admitted
OL,8,Ftwo counts of assaulting a police
OL,9,Fofficer.
OL,11,FA trial at Newport Crown Court heard
OL,12,Fthat shortly after the boys' death,
OL,13,Fthere was "grief, distress and anger"
OL,14,Fas a crowd gathered in Snowden Road,
OL,15,Fwhere the collision occurred on May
OL,16,F22, 2023.
