OL,3,CSix men found guilty of rioting in
OL,4,CEly, Cardiff, after deaths of teenage
OL,5,Cboys
OL,7,FThe court heard several police
OL,8,Fofficers were injured in the riot and
OL,9,Fresidents had their homes, vehicles
OL,10,Fand gardens damaged by rioters.
OL,12,FThe prosecutor said: "It's important
OL,13,Fto say the whole community didn't
OL,14,Fsupport or condone this extraordinary
OL,15,Fviolence. Amongst the footage there
OL,16,Fare occasional acts of kindness. They
OL,17,Fwere bewildered and frightened by what
OL,18,Fwas going on around them.
