OL,3,CSix men found guilty of rioting in
OL,4,CEly, Cardiff, after deaths of teenage
OL,5,Cboys
OL,7,F"Imagine sheltering in your own home
OL,8,Fwhilst mayhem unfolds in the street
OL,9,Foutside. Your car, garden and home
OL,10,Fbeing damaged by people appearing to
OL,11,Ftake a thrill out of abusing and
OL,12,Flaunching missiles at the police.
OL,14,F"The defendants, we say, played a part
OL,15,Fin that mayhem. The case against each
OL,16,Fof these defendants is principally
OL,17,Ffrom footage showing their
OL,18,Fparticipation in the riot."
